{"tid":1654412,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"Google Pixel 4 系列售價流出！最高階版或高達八千元","createTime":"2019-10-14T14:55:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-17T04:58:50.000Z","uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":27,"uniUserReply":49,"replies":[{"pid":"5a67d51889f2e23ee30340023fb501b090c65574","tid":1654412,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T14:55:54.000Z","msg":"iPhone 11、iPhone 11 Pro 及 iPhone 11 Pro Max 自開賣後，在不少國家及地區的銷售數字節節上升，走勢強勁，叫市場刮目相看。雖然已是 2019 年第四季，但仍有不少手機尚未登場，令人較期待的相信會是已定於 10 月 15 日在美國紐約發布的 Google Pixel 4 系列。說到 Pixel 4，其實 Google 於近幾個月來已將規格、外形、功能等毫無保留地 「流出」，只欠售價而已。<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2465000/2469130/10102019suet_02_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2465000%2F2469130%2F10102019suet_02_1024.jpg&h=4dc68da2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n<br />\nPixel 4 售價流出<br />\n定價高達 HK$8,000<br />\n10 月 15 日發布<br />\n<br />\n知名爆料者公開定價<br />\n<br />\n將於 10 月 15 日發布的 Google Pixel 4 系列，會有 Pixel 4 及 Pixel 4 XL 兩版本，隨着發布會時間臨近，有關於該機的消息網上愈傳愈多，可謂是完全沒有秘密，僅剩售價尚未公布。最近，知名爆料者 @evleaks 再度發放消息，指 Pixel 4 64GB 版售價為 CAD1049.95（約 HK$6,183.4）、128GB 版售 CAD1195.95（約 HK$7,043.22）；Pixel 4 XL 64GB 版定價與 Pixel 4 128GB 版本相同，同為 CAD1195.95，Pixel 4 XL 128GB 版則售 CAD1359.95（約 HK$8,009.06）。<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2465000/2469130/10102019suet_04_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2465000%2F2469130%2F10102019suet_04_600.jpg&h=b72d9ea8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n規格方面，Pixel 4 採用 5.7 吋 OLED 屏幕，配備 2,800mAh 電池；Pixel 4 XL 搭載 6.3 吋 OLED、3,700mAh 電池。其他規格方面，兩機均搭載 Snapdragon 855 處理器，6GB RAM、1,200 萬拍攝像素 + 1,600 萬拍攝像素雙主鏡頭、支援人臉解鎖等。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2469130/Google\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fezone.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Farticle%2F2469130%2FGoogle&d=ZEuQNtRgUz7rCGSUvjEm9wpem%2F37D4MqEuHX91B%2FZbc%3D&h=18f5f1aa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2469130/Google</a> Pixel 4 系列售價流出！最高階版或高達八千元"},{"pid":"0537c0246e73e05a4d51991538611b8738608eba","tid":1654412,"uid":22675,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T14:56:20.000Z","msg":"嘩, 咁貴, 真係同iphone11有得揮."},{"pid":"89599e5d75cbe65dcdc8ab849bbd3f7c354dd550","tid":1654412,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T14:56:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2469130/Google Pixel 4 系列售價流出！最高階版或高達八千元\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fezone.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Farticle%2F2469130%2FGoogle%20Pixel%204%20%E7%B3%BB%E5%88%97%E5%94%AE%E5%83%B9%E6%B5%81%E5%87%BA%EF%BC%81%E6%9C%80%E9%AB%98%E9%9A%8E%E7%89%88%E6%88%96%E9%AB%98%E9%81%94%E5%85%AB%E5%8D%83%E5%85%83&d=ZEuQNtRgUz7rCGSUvjEm9wpem%2F37D4MqEuHX91B%2FZbc%3D&h=42d4f86a\" target=\"_blank\">https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2469130/Google Pixel 4 系列售價流出！最高階版或高達八千元</a>"},{"pid":"9c52206f4a41f70bdb5f68cd38ca3d5cb412b38a","tid":1654412,"uid":37303,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T15:00:44.000Z","msg":"有無90hz"},{"pid":"46de5dcfdadbf55d69dd899c137b9c39f15a3aa1","tid":1654412,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9c52206f4a41f70bdb5f68cd38ca3d5cb412b38a","tid":1654412,"uid":37303,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T15:00:44.000Z","msg":"有無90hz"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T15:40:15.000Z","msg":"有"},{"pid":"8053e475ae72e3762ae898a6b40bdb8a565d78f4","tid":1654412,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T15:41:32.000Z","msg":"個鏡頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00ddfb32d31dfac93068803b6d70d922ccdc0a25","tid":1654412,"uid":135867,"like":21,"dislike":2,"score":19,"citedBy":1